  "translations": {
    "en": "The Commander of the Faithful (peace be upon him) said: \"Is this your supplication?\" The man said: \"You heard it?\" He said: \"Yes.\" The man said: \"Then recite it at the end of every prayer, for by Allah, no believer recites it except that Allah forgives his sins, even if they were as numerous as the stars and raindrops, and the pebbles and soil of the earth.\"",
